{"about_the_game":"<strong>Ergastulum</strong> is a first-person fantasy horror adventure game that blends a mix of <strong>Asian and Western folklore</strong> to create a terrifying vision that will test a player's faith to the extremes. The game focuses on psychological horror which relies on the character\u2019s fears and abnormal psyche to frighten players.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/598430/extras/F0AQyX7.gif?t=1697013231\" /><br><br>An Ergastulum is an underground building used to hold dangerous slaves, or other creatures. <i>This is the Dark World</i>. The player must traverse between Hell and Earth to find the answers they seek with the hope of rediscovering their faith which they have lost.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/598430/extras/vjS8BUi.gif?t=1697013231\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Full on horror experience not for the faint hearted<br></li><li>Stealth gameplay using the lights and shadows around you<br></li><li>Losing sanity affects your surroundings and how enemies react to the player<br></li><li>100% procedural-generated maps in the Dark World so every time you enter it will be the unknown<br></li><li>Inspired by both Western and Chinese folklore to create new forms of horror<br></li><li>Over 20 creatures each with their own unique traits<br></li><li>Plus MANY more untold secrets for you to discover</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/598430/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1697013231","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/598430/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1697013231","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/598430/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1697013231","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/598430